# ğŸ“ Student Marksheet System

A comprehensive console-based student grading and result management system developed in C programming language that automates the entire grading process for educational institutions.

## ğŸ“‹ Overview

The Student Marksheet System is a command-line application designed to streamline the academic evaluation process. It automatically calculates grades, generates performance feedback, and provides detailed academic analysis for students across multiple subjects.

## âœ¨ Key Features

- **ğŸ”„ Automated Grading**: Intelligent calculation of percentage and automatic grade assignment
- **ğŸ“ Dynamic Remarks**: Performance-based feedback generation system
- **ğŸ“Š Subject-wise Analysis**: Individual subject evaluation with pass/fail determination
- **ğŸ’» Clean Terminal Output**: Professional and neatly formatted result display
- **ğŸ·ï¸ Letter Grade Assignment**: Standard grading scale implementation (A+, A, B+, B, C+, C, D, F)
- **ğŸš¦ Pass/Fail Status Evaluation**: Comprehensive academic performance overview
- **ğŸ“ˆ CGPA Calculation**: Cumulative Grade Point Average computation
- **ğŸ¯ Performance Analytics**: Statistical analysis of student performance

